      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 52 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 52 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>艮，艮其背，不獲其身，行其庭，不見其人，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When one's resting is like that of the back, and he loses all consciousness of self; when he walks in his courtyard, and does not see any (of the persons) in it,--there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
