      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 52 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 52 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：艮其趾，无咎，利永貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject keeping his toes at rest. There will be no error; but it will be advantageous for him to be persistently firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
