      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 52 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 52 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：艮其腓，不拯其隨，其心不快。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows its subject keeping the calves of his legs at rest. He cannot help (the subject of the line above) whom he follows, and is dissatisfied in his mind.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
