      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：艮其輔，言有序，悔亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>S. The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject keeping his jawbones at rest, so that his words are (all) orderly. Occasion for repentance will disappear.</seg>
